  <brief_title>Intensive Combo Chemo With Autologous BM Rescue for Metastatic Breast Cancer</brief_title>
  <official_title>Intensive Combination Chemotherapy With Autologous Bone Marrow Rescue for Metastatic Breast Cancer After Intitial Cytoreduction With Standard Agents: A Phase II Study</official_title>
