  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      To determine the therapeutic efficacy of high-dose cyclophosphamide and BCNU with autologous
      bone marrow transplantation after initial tumor cytoreduction for patients with
      receptor-negative metastatic breast carcinoma and to determine the optimal timing of
      CyBCNU-ABMT after initial development of metastatic breast carcinoma
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
